definitions.definition: A suburb in the borough of Brent and borough of Camden , London , Greater London , England ( OS grid ref TQ245835 ) .
A village and civil parish in Amber Valley district, Derbyshire , England ( OS grid ref SK385455 ) .
A village in Kilburn High and Low parish, previously in Hambleton district, North Yorkshire , England , divided into High Kilburn and Low Kilburn ( OS grid ref SE512797 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
